OpenVPN Cookbook Chapter 9 sample code

The samples in this chapter are all openvpn configuration files, 
some server configuration files and some client configuration files.

Chapter 9 is divided up into 8 recipes. Below is a list of which
configuration file is used in which recipe.

9.1 Optimizing performance using 'ping'
none

9.2 Optimizing performance using 'iperf'
server: basic-udp-server.conf
client: basic-udp-client.conf

9.3 OpenSSL cipher speed
none

9.4 Compression tests
server: example9-4-server.conf
client1: example9-4-client.conf
client2: example9-4.ovpn

9.5 Traffic shaping
server: example9-5-server.conf
client: basic-udp-client.ovpn

9.6 Tuning UDP based connections
server: example9-6-server.conf
client: example9-6-client.conf

9.7 Tuning TCP based connections
server: example9-7-server.conf
client: example9-7.ovpn

9.8 Analyzing performance using tcpdump
server: example9-6-server.conf
client: example9-6-client.conf

